The paper focuses on cyber threat mitigation, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The proposed approach involves using machine learning techniques to predict attack sources, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the organization of allied organizations into coalitions, which involves network analysis and organization (cs.SI). The use of large datasets and experimentation with different partner selection strategies involves data science (cs.DS). Finally, the paper deals with privacy concerns, which is a key aspect of cybersecurity (cs.CY).
